Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.02,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{If you dare tell Sosuke...}Cậu mà dám nói với Sosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:27.05,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{You know all those novels and manga\N you hid in the clubroom?}Những cuốn manga và\N light novel cậu giấu ở phòng CLB...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:29.06,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'll mail them to your house,\N cash on delivery.}Tớ sẽ gửi hết về nhà cậu, ship COD luôn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.40,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Please, anything but—}Làm ơn đừng--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:33.32,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Wait, you found them?! \NThe ones at the back of the bookshelf?!}Cơ mà cậu tìm ra được à? Mấy cuốn tớ giấu sau giá sách?
