Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.62,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{A grown-up date.}Hẹn hò người lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:12.12,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Maybe he should give her flowers.}Nên tặng hoa nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.67,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,Hana Yori Dango. \N*Hình như tên một bộ manga"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.25,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,{Or better yet, after dark...}Hoặc là hơn nữa, đen tối hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:22.07,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,{may}{\alpha&HFF&\t(800,801,\alpha&H00&)}{be }{\alpha&HFF&\t(1600,1601,\alpha&H00&)}{give }{\alpha&HFF&\t(2400,2401,\alpha&H00&)}{her }{\alpha&HFF&\t(3150,3151,\alpha&H00&)}{\i1}{meat}{\i0}{.}Gái xôi thịt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.58,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I can't listen to her, either.}Cô ta quá nguy hiểm. Bỏ bỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:30.22,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,{But that seems a little premature \Nfor you, so here you go.}Nhưng với em thì còn hơi sớm, nhận cái này đi.
