Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.99,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Uh, maybe we should head home \Nbefore the trains get too crowded.}Chúng ta nên về nhà trước khi tàu điện đông đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.63,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{About that train ticket...}Tiền tàu về...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.89,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You don't have enough, do you?}Không có đủ à...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:02.73,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Right.}Ừm.
