Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.48,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Oh, there they are!}A, kia rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.26,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{You were riding the Ferris wheel?}Hai cậu lên vòng quay à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:14.43,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Wh-What were you doing together?}H-Hai người đã làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.08,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{We weren't doing anything.}Không làm gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.66,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Our friends would like to ride one more time!}Cho bọn em lên thêm vòng nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:28.62,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Okay. Now you're gonna tell \Nus what you were up to.}Rồi, giờ thì mau khai ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:32.92,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{"Up to"? We were riding the Ferris wheel.\N Nothing else happened.}Khai cái gì? Chỉ là ngồi cùng nhau thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:36.75,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{But I might have just lost my innocence.\N To Nukumizu-kun.}Tớ đã bị cướp mất sự trong trắng bởi cậu ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:40.80,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What?! I'm the one who was \Nprotecting your innocence!}Hả? Tớ mới là người bảo vệ nó cho cậu đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.85,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{What do you mean? Give us all the details!}Cái gì? Mau kể chi tiết xem nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.00,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{D-Drop dead!}C-Chết đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:49.29,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? L-Listen... I mean, uh...}À... chuyện là...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:02.05,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{That's the trouble with you, Nukumizu-kun.}Là như vậy đó, Nukumizu.
